		<hr size="1"></P><P>Well one must ask what your goals are.. is it to gain loot... or for a challenge.</P><P>On one hand if you never want to go to hate.. but push for fear raids.. you paint yourself a ugly shade of grey.</P><P>On the other hand, if you do the hate raids for what they are.. a cleric armor farming raid.. hehe you earn respect.</P><P>To the one who said the cog in the machine thing.  Yes.. its partially true.</P><P>As a cog however, one must spin faster than the others... You gotta shine.  I go to hate to KS the hell outta the melee.. I usually get plopped in the gimp group.. so its a challenge.. with the new changes to the planes.. Hate is a challenge.. the mini bosses are fun too.. 90% breastplate of the type to drop.. This means a couple things.. one.. the hate raids wont be needed as much as most people can get thier armor faster.. two, you get a chance to shine up your lures.  In your case.. Enticement of Flames</P><P>One hidden aspect many new planer wizards dont see.  Gems drop in hate.. A HELL OF ALOT more than Fear.</P><P>Go for the Diamonds and Blue Diamonds.. find a 250 Jeweler friend .. and make the following.</P><P>Golden Diamond Mask<BR>2 Electrum Blue Diamond Earrings<BR>2 Velium Diamond Rings<BR>2 Velium Blue Diamond Bracelets<BR>1 gold bluu diamond pendant<BR>1 platinum blue diamond tiara</P><P>when your done with that.. get these</P><P>1 electrum diamond mask (poison resists for trakanon)<BR>2 jacinch velium rings.. good MR for those purely MR encounters.</P><P><BR>As a wizard we have a job to do.. when people wanna kill gods, dragons.. uber things.. they call on the wizard.. (dont get me going on velious)  We are the slayers of dragons.. we need the saves to do our jobs</P><P>All saves should be 100+ unbuffed.  The more the better.. and the blue diamond stuff is +mana too.</P><P>To wear all these at once.. collect high int items per location.</P><P>1. Carmine Gloves<BR>2. Carmine Sleeves<BR>3. Golden Efreet Boots<BR>4. Ornate Rune Shield is nice.. +5 all saves too.. +8 int<BR>5.  Gnarled Staff from VS.. get wheel if yer not "uber" enough.</P><P>Always swap out gear for resist gear but try to keep your int at 200.  Tweak your setup till you can wear it all.</P><P>-----</P><P>Its the stupid reality that our armor drops in a plane they dont need us to get too.. You gotta think outside the box tho.</P><P>Get your Gems</P><P>Giblin<BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
